name: Angseri Villas
address: Banjar Tegeh No.108, Angseri, Kec. Baturiti, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82191, Indonesia
review 1: A lovely small hotel with only 5 separate small villas and there are also villas with a private pool. I lived in an ordinary villa with a shared infinity pool from which you have a beautiful view of the valley! The room is small but very cozy and clean, there is everything you need. Beautiful area and very friendly staff, great service. I had a wonderful time alone with myself and nature! I will definitely be back!
review 2: What a stunning place, incredible staff and service. The highlight is the floating pool overlooking plantation terraces.On a clear day you get a gorgeous view of the mountain. Lots of attractions close by, botanical gardens, luwak coffee tasting, waterfalls, temples, lakes...Food is delicious and bedding super comfortable.Totally worth a stay!
review 3: We are two families of 4 adults and 3 kids stayed in Villa no 06 for 1 nights. We have excellent night and the next day.
review 4: A very nice place to have some rest. The view is amazing, the staff is so nice and the food is great. Perfect adresse to discover the wild part of Bali.
review 5:
Amazing stay with angseri Villas !
we spend 5 days with my girlfriend, everything was perfect. the Room, view… everything is beautiful !
thanks a lot to the staff who take care of us ❤️
